%2C%20it's%20using%20cash%20from%20its%20recent%20%24275%20million%20fundraise%20to%20power%20acquisitions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rtorrence%40businessinsider.com%20(Rebecca%20Torrence)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finnovaccer-buying-startups-raising-secondaries-instead-of-ipo-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20Googlers%2C%20the%20pressure%20is%20on%20to%20use%20AI%20for%20everything%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20or%20get%20left%20behind%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227728%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22google%20ceo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a5ec70194a2d49b8aedae5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20addressed%20the%20crowd%20on%20May%2020%20at%20the%20company's%20annual%20I%2FO%20developers%20conference%20in%20Mountain%20View%2C%20California.%3Cp%3ECAMILLE%20COHEN%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20pressure%20has%20ramped%20up%20inside%20Google%20for%20employees%20to%20flex%20their%20AI%20muscles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20leaders%20told%20staff%20to%20be%20more%20AI-savvy%2C%20and%20engineers%20are%20now%20expected%20to%20use%20AI%20for%20coding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20staff%20expect%20their%20use%20of%20AI%20will%20be%20taken%20into%20account%20when%20performance%20reviews%20roll%20around.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Googlers%2C%20getting%20ahead%20at%20work%20doesn't%20just%20mean%20building%20AI.%20They're%20expected%20to%20work%20with%20it%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20pressure%20has%20ramped%20up%20inside%20Google%20for%20employees%20to%20use%20AI%20tools%20in%20their%20day-to-day%20work%20to%20make%20them%20more%20productive.%20As%20Google%20and%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-internal-memo-using-ai-no-longer-optional-github-copilot-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20giants%20like%20Microsoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20try%20to%20push%20the%20frontiers%20of%20AI%20for%20new%20products%2C%20they%20see%20ways%20it%20can%20boost%20their%20businesses%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20means%20getting%20employees%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20Google%20engineering%20vice%20president%20Megan%20Kacholia%20sent%20an%20email%20to%20software%20engineers%20telling%20them%20to%20use%20AI%20tools%20to%20improve%20their%20coding.%20The%20email%20also%20said%20that%20some%20engineer%20role%20profiles%E2%80%94a%20description%20of%20a%20specific%20job's%20tasks%20and%20duties%E2%80%94were%20being%20updated%20to%20include%20mentions%20of%20using%20AI%20to%20solve%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20July%20all-hands%20meeting%20with%20the%20whole%20company%2C%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20sent%20a%20simple%20message%20to%20the%20troops%3A%20Employees%20need%20to%20use%20AI%20for%20Google%20to%20lead%20this%20race%2C%20according%20to%20two%20employees%20who%20heard%20the%20remarks.%20Pichai%20said%20rival%20companies%20would%20leverage%20AI%2C%20so%20Google%20needs%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20does%20the%20same%20to%20compete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%2C%20which%20has%20been%20racing%20OpenAI%20and%20others%20with%20its%20Gemini%20AI%20models%2C%20is%20using%20internal%20learning%20programs%20to%20cajole%20staff%20into%20experimenting%20with%20vibe%20coding%20and%20using%20other%20AI%20tools%20to%20improve%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManagers%20have%20also%20been%20pushing%20staff%20to%20prove%20they're%20AI-savvy%2C%20according%20to%20several%20current%20employees%20who%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20because%20they%20were%20not%20permitted%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20employees%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20their%20managers%20have%20asked%20them%20to%20demonstrate%20how%20they%20use%20AI%20day-to-day%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20expect%20it%20will%20be%20taken%20into%20consideration%20when%20reviews%20do%20come%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20like%20a%20no-brainer%20that%20you%20need%20to%20be%20using%20it%20to%20get%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20predominantly%2C%20'Are%20you%20hitting%20your%20numbers%3F'%26quot%3B%20a%20sales%20employee%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you%20use%20AI%20to%20develop%20new%20workflows%20that%20others%20can%20use%20effectively%2C%20then%20that%20is%20rewarded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Google%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20while%20the%20company%20actively%20encourages%20Googlers%20to%20use%20AI%20in%20their%20daily%20work%2C%20it%20is%20not%20evaluating%20staff%20on%20it%20as%20part%20of%20their%20performance%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9c79bd6-eeee-4eda-9af4-b8b7b69f266e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20guidelines%20for%20Google%20engineers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKacholia's%20email%20to%20staff%20in%20June%20included%20a%20link%20to%20an%20updated%20set%20of%20guidelines%20on%20how%20engineers%20should%20use%20AI%20in%20their%20work.%20The%20guidelines%2C%20created%20by%20Google%20engineers%2C%20included%20best%20practices%20for%20how%20employees%20should%20and%20should%20not%20use%20AI%20for%20coding%20based%20on%20the%20capabilities%20of%20Google's%20internal%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngineers%20should%20use%20only%20internal%20models%20for%20coding%2C%20the%20guidelines%20said.%20Employees%20who%20want%20to%20use%20third-party%20AI%20tools%20for%20tasks%20outside%20coding%20must%20get%20approval%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20tech%20companies%20have%20similar%20rules%20to%20deter%20employees%20from%20putting%20sensitive%20internal%20information%20into%20outside%20systems.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-deploy-cursor-employee-interest-spikes-ai-coding-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22