20auto-generate%20assembly%20instructions%20for%20making%20complex%20machinery.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESiemens%20is%20teaming%20up%20with%20the%20startup%20to%20bring%20its%20AI%20build%20guides%20to%20customers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFounders%20Fund%20and%20Coatue%20are%20betting%20that%20AI%20can%20fix%20America's%20manufacturing%20bottlenecks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20ever%20had%20the%20pleasure%20of%20putting%20together%20furniture%2C%20you%20know%20how%20grueling%20it%20can%20be%20to%20squint%20at%20diagrams%20and%20guess%20which%20screw%20goes%20where.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20submarines%20and%20jet%20engines%20is%20certainly%20more%20complex%20than%20assembling%20a%20bed%20frame%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20assembly%20instructions%2C%20even%20the%20most%20advanced%20manufacturers%20sometimes%20face%20the%20same%20headache.%20One%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdefense-tech-china-american-manufacturing-reindustrialize-summit-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereindustrialization%3C%2Fa%3E-pilled%20startup%20thinks%20it%20has%20the%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20that%20paper%20instruction%20book%20that%20tells%20you%20how%20to%20build%20something%3F%26quot%3B%20Fil%20Aronshtein%2C%20Dirac's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20asked%2C%20referencing%20a%20harrowing%20experience%20with%20an%20Ikea%20bookshelf.%20%26quot%3BIt%20turns%20out%20everything%20around%20us%20also%20needs%20assembly%20instructions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAronshtein%20says%20BuildOS%2C%20Dirac's%20main%20product%2C%20is%20a%20software%20tool%20that%20uses%20AI%20to%20generate%20assembly%20instructions%20for%20manufacturers.%20The%20startup%20raised%20nearly%20%2411%20million%20from%20Founders%20Fund%20and%20Coatue%20Management%20%E2%80%94%20and%20struck%20a%20new%20partnership%20with%20industrial%20manufacturing%20giant%20Siemens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20the%20workflow%20for%20building%20a%20piece%20of%20hard%20tech%20goes%20something%20like%20this%3A%20%26quot%3BSome%20dude%20gets%20a%20CAD%20file%20over%20email%2C%20takes%20hundreds%20of%20screenshots%20manually%2C%20figures%20out%20what%20order%20to%20do%20the%20assembly%2C%20then%20takes%20all%20those%20screenshots%20and%20throws%20them%20together%20into%20a%20100-page%20PowerPoint%2C%26quot%3B%20Aronshtein%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20super%20manual%2C%20and%20super%20tedious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20relying%20on%20humans%20to%20stitch%20together%20those%20convoluted%20instructions%2C%20the%2018-person%20startup%20says%20it%20uses%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20determine%20the%20order%20of%20assembly.%20(Aronshtein%20declined%20to%20disclose%20whether%20the%20company%20uses%20a%20foundation%20model%20or%20trains%20its%20own.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Aronshtein%20cofounded%20Dirac%20with%20Peter%20Weiss%2C%20a%20college%20friend%20who%20briefly%20worked%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20Amazon.%20Aronshtein%20had%20a%20short%20stint%20at%20Northrop%20Grumman.%20The%20two%20met%20as%20electrical%20engineering%20undergrads%20at%20Johns%20Hopkins%2C%20where%20they%20both%20earned%20master's%20degrees%20in%20robotics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Siemens%20partnership%20under%20its%20belt%2C%20Dirac%20is%20integrating%20BuildOS%20with%20Teamcenter%2C%20Siemens'%20engineering%20management%20software.%20That%20integration%20will%20allow%20Dirac%20to%20work%20more%20closely%20with%20Siemens'%20customer%20base%2C%20said%20Tomas%20Klausing%2C%20a%20director%20of%20technology%20partnerships%20at%20Siemens.%20(Aronshtein%20wouldn't%20name%20customers%20but%20said%20Dirac%20is%20working%20with%20%26quot%3Bsome%20of%20the%20coolest%20companies%20on%20the%20planet%20in%20aerospace%2C%20defense%2C%20automotive%2C%20agriculture%2C%20construction%2C%20machinery%2C%20and%20maritime.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDirac%20isn't%20the%20only%20company%20trying%20to%20modernize%20the%20shop%20floor.%20Tulip%2C%20a%20manufacturing%20software%20startup%20that%20last%20raised%20%24100%20million%20in%202021%2C%20is%20also%20making%20software%20for%20machinery%20with%20a%20platform%20that%20aims%20to%20track%20factory%20production%20and%20equipment%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220077b01a-ebf5-4842-84f3-4937d03d69ef%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Capacity%20to%20Build'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20Dirac's%20origin%20story%20is%20tied%20to%20Silicon%20Valley's%20recent%20push%20to%20%26quot%3Breindustrialize%26quot%3B%20the%20US%2C%20a%20movement%20aimed%20at%20reshoring%20production%20and%20keeping%20pace%20with%20China's%20blistering%20industrial%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20foundation%20of%20the%20West%20was%20built%20upon%20our%20capacity%20to%20build%2C%26quot%3B%20Aronshtein%20said.%20But%20during%20his%20time%20at%20Northrop%20Grumman%2C%20he%20was%20struck%20by%20how%20%26quot%3Bridiculously%20archaic%20all%20of%20the%20infrastructure%20was%20on%20the%20manufacturing%20side%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20something%20he%20wanted%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20insight%20came%20as%20funding%20for%20defense%20tech%20startups%20was%20surging.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-mafia-former-employees-startups-anduril-2025-3%23trae-stephens-matt-grimm-and-brian-schimpf-anduril-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrae%20Stephens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPeter%20Thiel's%20Founders%20Fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-palmer-luckey%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnduril%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bet%20on%20Dirac%20after%20seeing%20firsthand%20how%20much%20the%20defense%20industry%20hinged%20on%20US-based%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20America's%20factories%20up%20to%20speed%20has%20become%20a%20recent%20obsession%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%