none%20felt%20right.%20That%20is%2C%20until%20Derek.%20He%20was%20eccentric%2C%20calm%2C%20empathetic%2C%20unfazed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-dad-was-diagnosed-with-dementia-hes-slipping-away-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDad's%20unpredictable%20behavior%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20he%20spoke%20directly%20to%20him%20(something%20few%20people%20did%20anymore).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20two%20years%2C%20Derek%20offered%20companionship%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20structure.%20I%20moved%20into%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-afford-live-alone-roommate-loneliness-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20solo%20apartment%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20city%2080%20miles%20away%20so%20I%20could%20visit%20on%20weekends.%20However%2C%20I%20carried%20a%20lot%20of%20guilt%2C%20especially%20when%20my%20dad%20sent%20me%20texts%20asking%20me%20to%20move%20back%20in%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Derek%20shared%20that%20my%20dad%20was%20declining.%20When%20I%20returned%20home%20from%20travels%20abroad%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20find%20my%20dad%20barely%20speaking%20and%20no%20longer%20engaging%20in%20his%20old%20routines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20with%20her%20father%20on%20a%20lawn%2C%20looking%20at%20a%20few%20fish%20inside%20a%20circled%20up%20hose.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a4c63a194a2d49b8aecdf8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20the%20time%20came%2C%20they%20moved%20him%20to%20a%20care%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alice%20Draper%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273edbfaf-f562-49ea-97be-dd443a093a31%5C%22%3EWe%20moved%20my%20dad%20into%20a%20care%20home%20for%20people%20with%20dementia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20phoned%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alz.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlzheimer's%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they%20sent%20me%20a%20spreadsheet%20with%20hundreds%20of%20care%20homes%20in%20the%20area.%20I%20screened%20all%20of%20them%20and%20visited%20the%20short-listed%20homes%20with%20my%20mom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20stomach%20sank%20on%20these%20visits%20when%20I%20saw%20the%20sterile%20and%20soulless%20hospital%20atmosphere.%20But%20eventually%2C%20we%20found%20a%20home%20for%20people%20with%20dementia%20that%20was%20less%20depressing%20than%20the%20others.%20The%20staff%20were%20friendly%2C%20and%20the%20residents%20roamed%20freely%20around%20the%20property.%20The%20room%20available%20had%20a%20door%20leading%20into%20the%20courtyard%2C%20where%20my%20dad%20could%20freely%20smoke%2C%20and%20they%20let%20him%20bring%20his%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20dad%20was%20almost%20nonverbal%20by%20then%2C%20on%20the%20day%20we%20moved%20him%2C%20he%20became%20coherent%20and%20engaged%20in%20two-way%20dialogues%20(something%20he%20hadn't%20done%20in%20years).%20He%20was%20scared%20and%20angry%2C%20and%20pleaded%20with%20me%20and%20Derek%20not%20to%20leave%20him%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20with%20her%20father%20and%20grandmother%20at%20her%2021st%20birthday%2C%20dressed%20up%20in%20front%20of%20a%20backdrop%20of%20playing%20cards.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a4c846cfc04e97619ba733%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20father%20and%20grandmother%20both%20attended%20her%2021st%20birthday.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alice%20Draper%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c60c719a-d91c-4609-8ea5-2fcecd0cecc0%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20the%20right%20choice%2C%20but%20I%20still%20feel%20some%20guilt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELogically%2C%20I%20knew%20moving%20him%20was%20the%20best%20decision.%20But%20my%20emotions%20said%20something%20else.%20I%20remember%20bending%20over%20by%20the%20tree%20outside%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-dementia-changed-person-holidays-hard-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecare%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20trying%20to%20quell%20my%20guilt-induced%20nausea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20father%20still%20lives%20in%20this%20care%20home%2C%20and%20I%20am%20now%20certain%20this%20was%20the%20right%20decision.%20He%20has%20constant%20companionship%20from%20other%20residents%20and%20the%2024-hour%20care%20that%20he%20needs.%20I%20have%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-abroad-made-life-better-but-did-not-fix-everything-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20visit%20him%20every%20few%20months%20when%20I%20am%20home.%20While%20he%20doesn't%20remember%20me%2C%20I%20can%20tell%20that%20he%20is%20well%20cared%20for.%20He%20eats%20meals%20with%20others%2C%20many%20residents%20know%20him%20by%20name%20and%20offer%20him%20snacks%20and%20cigarettes%2C%20and%20the%20staff%20are%20attentive%20to%20his%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20care%20home's%20%26quot%3Bopen%20door%20policy%26quot%3B%20for%20visitation%20gives%20me%20peace%20of%20mind%2C%20as%20I%20always%20drop%20in%20unannounced.%20I%20also%20think%20that%20the%20amount%20of%20human%20contact%20he%20receives%20has%20slowed%20down%20his%20deterioration%2C%20since%20previously%20neither%20Derek%20nor%20I%20were%20around%20him%2024%2F7.%20However%2C%20I%20still%20feel%20bouts%20of%20anxiety%20about%20him%2C%20and%20my%20mother%20regularly%20visits%20and%20gives%20me%20updates%20while%20I%20am%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'm%20not%20sure%20my%20feelings%20of%20guilt%20will%20ever%20go%20away%2C%20I%20try%20to%20remind%20myself%20that%20I%20am%20living%20the%20life%20that%20my%20pre-dementia%20father%20would%20have%20wanted%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%