under%20says%20Wall%20Street%20is%20missing%20great%20hires%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeff%20Aronson%2C%20Co-Founder%20and%20Managing%20Principal%20of%20Centerbridge%20Partners%20headshot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a68967cfc04e97619bbf16%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223392%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeff%20Aronson%2C%20co-founder%20and%20managing%20principal%20of%20Centerbridge%20Partners.%3Cp%3EMike%20Blake%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWall%20Street%20is%20overlooking%20talent%20by%20focusing%20on%20Ivy%20League%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%2C%20said%20investor%20Jeff%20Aronson.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAronson%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Centerbridge%20Partners%2C%20prizes%20curiosity%20and%20independent%20thinking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe's%20partnered%20with%20CUNY%20to%20tap%20overlooked%20talent%20%E2%80%94%20a%20win%20for%20students%20and%20the%20finance%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fwall-street%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWall%20Street's%3C%2Fa%3E%20best%20hires%20don't%20look%20anything%20like%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20it%20worships%2C%20said%20Jeff%20Aronson%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Centerbridge%20Partners%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fprivate-equity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprivate%20equity%3C%2Fa%3E%20firm%20managing%20more%20than%20%2442%20billion%20in%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20joke%20with%20people%20I%20couldn't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fhiring%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eget%20a%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20my%20own%20firm%2C%26quot%3B%20Aronson%20said%20in%20the%20Goldman%20Sachs%20%26quot%3BExchanges%26quot%3B%20podcast%20on%20July%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20go%20to%20an%20Ivy%20League%20school.%20I%20didn't%20graduate%20Phi%20Beta%20Kappa.%20I%20don't%20speak%20six%20languages.%20I%20didn't%20discover%20the%20cure%20for%20cancer%20when%20I%20was%20nine%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20recording%20uploaded%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAronson%20came%20up%20through%20Johns%20Hopkins%2C%20where%20he%20earned%20a%20BA%20with%20honors%2C%20and%20NYU%20School%20of%20Law%2C%20a%20path%20outside%20the%20Ivy%20League%20track%20that%20dominates%20Wall%20Street%20recruiting.%20US%20News%20and%20World%20Report%20ranks%20Baltimore-based%20Johns%20Hopkins%20sixth%20on%20its%20top%20national%20universities%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20is%20often%20stereotyped%20as%20an%20Ivy%20League%20stronghold.%20But%20data%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-bank-employee-demographic-front-office-education-race-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERevelio%20Labs%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20that%20only%2011.7%25%20of%20New%20York-based%20front-office%20workers%20at%20top%20firms%20%E2%80%94%20including%20JPMorgan%20Chase%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20and%20Citigroup%20%E2%80%94%20graduated%20from%20Ivy-plus%20schools%2C%20defined%20as%20the%20Ivy%20League%20plus%20Chicago%2C%20Stanford%2C%20Duke%2C%20and%20MIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Aronson%2C%20credentials%20aren't%20what%20make%20someone%20a%20great%20investor.%20What%20matters%20is%20mindset%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAttributes%2C%20it's%20the%20same%20thing%20that%20you%20folks%20look%20for%3A%20people%20who%20are%20smart%20and%20hardworking%20and%20driven%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20also%20prizes%20people%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Breally%20intellectually%20curious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20partly%20why%20he%20believes%20Wall%20Street%20keeps%20overlooking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epromising%20talent.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we're%20all%20scrambling%20and%20tripping%20over%20ourselves%2C%20looking%20for%20the%20same%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Aronson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20real%20edge%20comes%20from%20hiring%20those%20who%20think%20independently%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20asking%20candidates%20whether%20they%20compared%20notes%20with%20friends%20on%20the%20buy%20side%20%E2%80%94%20a%20question%20he%20phrased%20to%20encourage%20a%20%26quot%3Byes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20he%20actually%20wanted%20to%20hear%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20because%20he%20wanted%20people%20who%20would%20do%20their%20own%20work%2C%20and%20make%20their%20own%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20contrarian%20streak%20has%20also%20shaped%20where%20he%20looks%20for%20talent.%20Rather%20than%20only%20competing%20for%20the%20same%20Ivy%20League%20graduates%20as%20every%20other%20firm%2C%20Aronson%20also%20turned%20his%20attention%20to%20the%20City%20University%20of%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20240%2C000%20degree-program%20students%2C%20CUNY%20is%20the%20largest%20public%20urban%20university%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20one%20that%20few%20Wall%20Street%20recruiters%20seriously%20consider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20met%20some%20of%20these%20kids%2C%20and%20they%20were%20smart%20and%20they%20were%20hardworking.%20But%20you%20know%20what%20else%20they%20had%3F%20They%20had%20grit.%20There%20was%20no%20millennial%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZero.%20They%20had%20grit.%20Most%20of%20them%20worked%20their%20way%20through%20school.%20And%20so%20we%20started%20hiring%20them.%20And%20all%20they%20wanted%20%E2%80%94%20it%20reminded%20me%20a%20little%20like%20when%20I%20started.%20'I%20just%20want%20a%20chance.%20Give%20me%20a%20chance%2C'%26quot%3B%20Aronson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20started%20hiring%20these%20kids%2C%20and%20they%20were%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalling%20CUNY%20%26quot%3Bthe%20undiscovered%20jewel%20that%20no%20one's%20thinking%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20Aronson%20has%20partnered%20with%20John%20Waldron%2C%20president%20of%20Goldman%2C%20and%20billionaire%20Mike%20Bloomberg%20to%20invest%20millions%20into%20programs%20linking%20its%20students%20with%20finance%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%2C%20he%20added%2C%20has%20been%20a%20win%20for%20everyone%20involved%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20a%20huge%20win%20for%20these%20students.%20It's%20been%20great%20for%20New%20York%20City.%20And%20it's%20been%20smart%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-talent-hiring-resume-centerbridge-investor-jeff-aronson-cuny-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755758023000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a689eaa17a8c5b4053347c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-talent-hiring-resume-centerbridge-investor-jeff-aronson-cuny-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Grit%20and%20curiosity%20matter%20more%20than%20pedigree%2C%20says%20Jeff%20Aronson%2C%20managing%20principal%20of%20Centerbridge%20Partners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-talent-hiring-resume-centerbridge-investor-jeff-aronson-cuny-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PPP%20must%20drive%20India's%20infrastructure%20funding%3A%20Experts%20at%20BS%20Infra%20Summit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755757442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-08%2F21%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1755757345-1329.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fspecials%2Fb