%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fparentsmurder-case-1989-menendez-brothers-to-face-parole-hearing-after-30-years-in-prison-will-appear-via-videoconferencing-from-san-diego%2Famp_articleshow%2F123424305.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fparentsmurder-case-1989-menendez-brothers-to-face-parole-hearing-after-30-years-in-prison-will-appear-via-videoconferencing-from-san-diego%2Famp_articleshow%2F123424305.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Poland%20says%20air%20defenses%20didn't%20detect%20a%20Russian%20drone%20entering%20its%20airspace%2C%20and%20that%20it%20only%20realized%20in%20the%20morning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Polish%20Mi-24%20flies%20during%20a%20defense%20exercise%20in%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a69129194a2d49b8aee68d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221896%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Polish%20general%20said%20the%20country%20activated%20its%20%26quot%3Bentire%20target%20detection%20system%20%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20Mi-24%20helicopter%20patrol%2C%20but%20stood%20down%20after%20roughly%20two%20hours%20on%20Tuesday%20evening.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20they%20discovered%20a%20Russian%20drone%20had%20crashed%20in%20a%20cornfield.%3Cp%3EKACPER%20PEMPEL%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Polish%20general%20said%20a%20Russian%20drone%20crashed%20in%20Poland%20despite%20air%20defenses%20being%20activated%20at%20night.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20authorities%20only%20received%20information%20about%20the%20drone%20crash%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20drone%20likely%20had%20a%20Chinese%20engine%20and%20was%20flying%20%26quot%3Bvery%20low%26quot%3B%20to%20avoid%20detection.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWarsaw%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20a%20Russian%20drone%20crashed%20and%20exploded%20in%20a%20field%20in%20eastern%20Poland%2C%20and%20that%20the%20uncrewed%20system%20was%20only%20discovered%20the%20morning%20after%20air%20defenses%20were%20activated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20was%20injured%2C%20but%20Poland's%20defense%20minister%2C%20W%C5%82adys%C5%82aw%20Kosiniak-Kamysz%2C%20called%20the%20incident%20a%20provocation%20against%20NATO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussia%20is%20once%20again%20provoking%20NATO%20countries%20following%20drone%20incidents%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20Romania%2C%20Lithuania%2C%20Latvia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20accusing%20the%20Kremlin%20of%2010%20total%20airspace%20violations%20since%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20officials%20said%20the%20drone%20likely%20entered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-deploying-dutch-norway-f35-poland-air-defense-ukraine-russia-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPolish%20airspace%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20or%20Wednesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen.%20Dariusz%20Malinowski%2C%20deputy%20commander%20of%20Poland's%20Armed%20Forces%20Operational%20Command%2C%20said%20air%20defenses%20were%20put%20on%20alert%20that%20evening%20during%20one%20of%20Russia's%20nightly%20drone%20and%20missile%20waves%20against%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWarsaw%20regularly%20activates%20its%20air%20defenses%20along%20its%20border%20as%20a%20precaution%20during%20such%20attacks%2C%20especially%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoland-missile-us-russia-ukraine-nato-response-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estray%20Ukrainian%20defensive%20missile%3C%2Fa%3E%20killed%20two%20Polish%20citizens%20in%20November%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalinowski%20said%20Polish%20air%20defenses%20were%20alerted%20at%2010%20p.m.%20on%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20alongside%20%26quot%3Bstandard%20measures%20designed%20to%20seal%20our%20border.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20target%20detection%20system%20was%20activated.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20forces%20and%20means%20for%20countering%20missiles%20were%20put%20on%20combat%20readiness%2C%20and%20a%20Mi-24%20helicopter%20was%20also%20raised%2C%20which%20patrolled%20the%20eastern%20part%2C%20the%20Ukrainian%20part%20of%20our%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20midnight%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoland-growing-military-arsenal-nato-ukraine-russia-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPolish%20military%3C%2Fa%3E%20stood%20down%20because%20it%20had%20not%20detected%20any%20abnormalities%20or%20threats%2C%20Malinowski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20had%20happened%20that%20would%20show%20us%20that%20something%20was%20out%20of%20the%20ordinary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20authorities%20found%20out%20in%20the%20morning%20that%20a%20drone%20had%20exploded%20in%20a%20cornfield%20in%20Osiny%2C%20a%20village%20nearly%2070%20miles%20from%20Poland's%20border%20with%20Ukraine%20and%20roughly%20400%20miles%20from%20mainland%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20morning%2C%20after%20sunrise%2C%20we%20received%20information%2C%20as%20has%20already%20been%20said%20here%2C%20about%20an%20object%20that%20exploded%20very%20close%20to%20%C5%81uk%C3%B3w%2C%26quot%3B%20Malinowski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e2bc1c6d-91c6-4c44-b99b-d9173023f766%5C%22%3EA%20stealthy%20decoy%20drone%20with%20Chinese%20parts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20said%20that%20preliminary%20investigations%20indicated%20the%20drone%20was%20%26quot%3Bflying%20very%20low%26quot%3B%20to%20avoid%20radar%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20assessment%2C%20this%20drone%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20detect%2C%20and%20that%20is%20indeed%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Malinowski%20also%20said%20that%20it's%20still%20unclear%20if%20the%20drone%20was%20flown%20deliberately%20into%20Poland.%20Neither%20is%20it%20immediately%20clear%20exactly%20when%20the%20drone%20entered%20Polish%20airspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20did%20not%20confirm%20the%20drone's%20flight%20path.%20A%20drone%20launched%20from%20mainland%20Russia%20would%20have%20to%20pass%20through%20either%20Belarus%20or%20Ukraine%20to%20enter%20Polish%20airspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinland-joining-nato-means-russia-baltic-kaliningrad-more-isolated-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKaliningrad%2C%20a%20militarized%20Russian%20exclave%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sits%20directly%20on%20Poland's%20northern%20border%2C%20though%20it's%20unclear%20if%20investigators%20think%20the%20drone%20launch%20may%20have%20originated%20from%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalinowski%20added%20that%20while%20search%20teams%20were%20still%20collecting%20the%20drone's%20remains%2C%20initial%20evidence%20pointed%20to%20it%20being%20equipped%20with%20a%20Chinese%20engine%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bself-destructive%20warhead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20mean%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-intensifies-use-of-decoy-drones-against-ukraine-isw-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrone%20was%20a%20decoy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Russia%20commonly%20deploys%20the%20Shahed%2C%20a%20long-range%20attack%20drone%20designed%20by%20Iran.%20One%20of%20its%20locally%20produced%20versions%2C%20called%20the%20Gerbera%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20mimic%20the%20loitering%20munition's%20signature%20and%20appearance%20while%20carrying%20a%20much%20weaker%20warhead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReuters%20cited%20a%20Polish%20defense%20ministry%20spokesperson%20saying%20that%20the%20crashed%20drone%20was%20a%20Russian%20version%20of%20the%20Shahed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20forces%20have%20long%20said%20that%20they%20often%20find%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-level-up-shahed-drones-chinese-antenna-bypass-jammers-2025-3%5C%22