lt%3D%5C%22They%20had%20a%20choice%20of%20original%20or%20strawberry%20matcha.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a5661f194a2d49b8aed4a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20had%20a%20choice%20of%20original%20or%20strawberry%20matcha.%20I%20chose%20the%20second.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStepping%20out%20of%20Singapore's%2090-degree%20heat%2C%20the%20iced%20matcha%20was%20a%20welcome%20treat.%20At%20least%2020%20people%20waited%20to%20get%20to%20the%20counter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20matcha%20with%20strawberry%20jam%20was%20nicely%20balanced%2C%20sweet%20and%20bitter%2C%20and%20it%20went%20down%20all%20too%20quickly.%20There%20was%20also%20a%20bar%20outside%20the%20main%20party%20venue%2C%20where%20people%20could%20buy%20other%20drinks%20at%20their%20own%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatcha%2C%20made%20almost%20exclusively%20in%20Japan%20from%20green%20tea%20leaves%2C%20has%20exploded%20in%20popularity%20globally%20and%20become%20a%20TikTok%20obsession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20so%20popular%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20Japanese%20suppliers%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktoks-obsession-matcha-created-shortage-tea-japan-social-media-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efretting%20over%20a%C2%A0shortage%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20cope%20with%20the%20overwhelming%C2%A0supply%2C%20suppliers%20have%20raised%20prices%20and%20set%20order%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20long%20queue%20for%20the%20complimentary%20matcha%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223655%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20queue%20for%20the%20complimentary%20matcha%20was%20about%2020%20people%20long%20when%20I%20arrived.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a565efa17a8c5b405322bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222769%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20queue%20for%20the%20complimentary%20matcha%20was%20about%2020%20people%20long%20when%20I%20arrived.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20plenty%20of%20matcha%20at%20the%20rave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGill%2C%20the%2023-year-old%20organizer%20who%20graduated%20from%20Singapore's%20Nanyang%20Technological%20University%20last%20year%2C%20said%20she%20wanted%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20hype%20and%20attract%20people%20who%20love%20the%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20worked.%20Yuhan%20Aw%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20college%20student%20who%20attended%20the%20event%20with%20her%20friends%2C%20said%20she's%20become%20obsessed%20with%20matcha%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20with%20a%20love%20of%20matcha%20ice%20cream%20soon%20became%20a%20lifestyle%20%E2%80%94%20she's%20bought%20the%20whisk%2C%20bowl%2C%20powder%2C%20and%20everything%20needed%20to%20brew%20her%20own%20cups%20of%20strawberry%20and%20mango%20matcha%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20while%20she%20enjoyed%20an%20occasional%20night%20out%20with%20drinks%2C%20she%20was%20happy%20to%20try%20an%20alternative%20form%20of%20partying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20Singapore.%20Younger%20people%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-sober-non-alcoholic-economy-restaurants-events-boom-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrinking%20less%20booze.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20a%20Gallup%20poll%20on%20alcohol%20consumption%20trends%20released%20on%20August%2013%2C%20the%20number%20of%20adults%20in%20the%20US%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2018%20to%2035%20who%20reported%20that%20they%20drink%20alcohol%20fell%20from%2059%25%20in%202023%20to%2050%25%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EParty%20hard%2C%20go%20to%20sleep%20early%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mix%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials%20danced%20to%20tunes%20by%20Bad%20Bunny%2C%20Tyla%2C%20and%20other%20artists.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a566c6194a2d49b8aed4ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20mix%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials%20danced%20to%20tunes%20by%20Bad%20Bunny%2C%20Tyla%2C%20and%20other%20artists.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attendees%2C%20a%20mix%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials%2C%20came%20ready%20to%20rave%2C%20dressed%20in%20everything%20from%20sage%20green%20linen%20to%20latex%20bustier%20tops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20danced%20to%20mixes%20by%20local%20DJs%20%E2%80%94%20Vijay%20Singh%2C%20Liana%20Azman%2C%20and%20Shahan%2C%20Gill's%20co-organizer.%20Shahan%2C%2024%2C%20has%20been%20working%20in%20the%20Singapore%20nightlife%20scene%20for%20years%2C%20organizing%20events%20and%20DJing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20music%20was%20a%20blend%20of%20pop%20and%20EDM%2C%20and%20the%20highlight%20of%20the%20evening%20for%20me%20was%20a%20fiery%20remix%20of%20South%20African%20singer%20Tyla's%20TikTok-famous%20song%20from%202024%2C%20%26quot%3BWater.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20night%20out%20in%20Singapore%20is%20costly%20and%20taxing%2C%20Shahan%20said.%20Public%20transport%20in%20the%20city%20largely%20stops%20after%20midnight%2C%20meaning%20clubbers%20need%20to%20take%20a%20cab%20home.%20And%20the%20country's%20alcohol%20taxes%20are%20among%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaytime%2C%20sober%20parties%20like%20the%20matcha%20rave%20solved%20many%20of%20those%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20actually%20make%20proper%20connections%20and%20friends%20this%20way%2C%20compared%20to%20when%20you're%20drunk%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BOn%20top%20of%20all%20that%2C%20you're%20still%20able%20to%20go%20for%20dinner%20after%2C%20and%20be%20in%20bed%20by%2010%20p.m.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERayve%20Chai%2C%20a%2039-year-old%20analyst%20who%20attended%20the%20matcha%20rave%2C%20said%20he%20wasn't%20a%20huge%20matcha%20fan.%20But%20he