CThe%20same%20boy%20who%E2%80%99d%20been%20bunking%20PE%20(physical%20education)%20class%20in%20school%20now%20practises%20for%20hours%20in%20the%20hot%20summer%20sun.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20resolve%20was%20tested%20during%20his%20training%20period%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20games%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20train%20for%20three%20hours%20on%20weekdays%2C%20seven%20hours%20on%20weekends%2C%20and%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20day%20during%20the%20summer%20holidays.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20medal%20%E2%80%94%20much%20less%20upending%20expectations%20by%20winning%20three%20%E2%80%94%20was%20never%20on%20the%20cards.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20always%20told%20me%20to%20go%20have%20fun%20at%20the%20games%3B%20%E2%80%98try%20winning%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20said%2C%20but%20I%20remember%20when%20I%20held%20the%20first%20gold%20medal%2C%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20what%20I%E2%80%99d%20actually%20managed.%20My%20mother%20was%20crying%3B%20her%20kidney%2C%20after%20all%2C%20had%20helped%20me%20do%20something%20significant%20for%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varun%20shares.%20Varun%20is%20set%20to%20participate%20once%20again%20in%20the%20ongoing%20games.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-1-1755520390.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varun%20and%20his%20mother%20Deepa%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20kidney%20donor%20for%20Varun's%20transplant%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-1-1755520390.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-1-1755520390-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-1-1